&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;This is a senior individual contributor role. You won&#39;t manage a team. Your leverage is craft, not headcount. You&#39;ll work directly with the VP and partner with Staff Designers across tribes – connecting their context into something coherent at the division level, and building the systems that raise the ceiling for everyone doing design work at Mews.&lt;/p&gt;
