&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Partner with Staff Designers so that tribe-level design substrates compose into a coherent whole rather than a collection of parallel efforts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Act as the VP&#39;s right hand on the most complex cross-tribe design problems – the ones that don&#39;t fit neatly inside any single tribe&#39;s scope.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Contribute craft feedback and calibration input into Director and Staff Designer performance reviews.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Encode judgment into systems. Turn design thinking into reusable leverage – components, tokens, patterns, agents, shared skills – rather than one-off artifacts that live and die with a single project.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
