&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Let&#39;s get into the specifics. It’s impossible to capture every nuance of a role – especially at a rapidly growing company like Mews – but if we had to distil it into a job description (which we do because this is a job description), it would be this:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;wnfdntd&quot; data-pm-slice=&quot;1 1 []&quot;&gt;Mews has been transforming hospitality since 2012, building a connected hospitality cloud that powers thousands of properties worldwide. As part of this journey, we’re scaling Mews&#39; FinTech offering and we’re looking for a Risk Manager to build and own our enterprise risk framework from the ground up. This is a senior, hands-on role based in the Netherlands, reporting directly to our Chief Risk &amp;amp; Compliance Officer (CRCO). You’ll sit at the intersection of payments, regulation and product, working closely with first-line teams, the MLRO and Management Board. If you’re currently managing a slice of the risk universe (e.g. financial or operational risk) and want full enterprise-wide ownership in a greenfield environment, this is for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;wnfdntd&quot; data-pm-slice=&quot;1 1 []&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;heading 2&quot;&gt;✅&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;heading 2&quot;&gt; Your mission, should you choose to accept it:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134245418&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134245529&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:40}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;_1bdmgj40 _1ibi0s312 _1ibi0s31i _1llyo9u0 focusable-list-item&quot; data-ui-element=&quot;chat-assistant-content-bubble&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;_1ibi0s312 _1ibi0s31i _1ibi0s31y&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;p8i6j07 p8i6j02&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p8i6j0a&quot;&gt;Own and run the ERM framework and risk appetite for Mews FS, including risk assessments, stress testing and Board reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p8i6j0a&quot;&gt;Provide independent risk oversight on new products, major changes and strategic initiatives, and act as a key contact for DNB and other regulators on risk matters.&lt;/li&gt;
