&lt;p&gt;Let&#39;s get into the specifics. It’s impossible to capture every nuance of a role – especially at a rapidly growing company like Mews – but if we had to distil it into a job description (which we do because this is a job description), it would be this:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;First Paragraph&quot; data-ccp-parastyle-defn=&quot;{&amp;quot;ObjectId&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;276295ed-5df2-5456-988c-5fdbab071054|1&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;ClassId&amp;quot;:1073872969,&amp;quot;Properties&amp;quot;:[201342446,&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;,201342447,&amp;quot;5&amp;quot;,201342448,&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;,201342449,&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;,469777841,&amp;quot;Aptos&amp;quot;,469777842,&amp;quot;Arial&amp;quot;,469777843,&amp;quot;Aptos&amp;quot;,469777844,&amp;quot;Aptos&amp;quot;,201341986,&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;,469769226,&amp;quot;Aptos,Arial&amp;quot;,268442635,&amp;quot;24&amp;quot;,335559739,&amp;quot;180&amp;quot;,335559738,&amp;quot;180&amp;quot;,469775450,&amp;quot;First Paragraph&amp;quot;,201340122,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;,134234082,&amp;quot;true&amp;quot;,134233614,&amp;quot;true&amp;quot;,469778129,&amp;quot;FirstParagraph&amp;quot;,335572020,&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;,469775498,&amp;quot;Body Text&amp;quot;,469778324,&amp;quot;Body Text&amp;quot;]}&quot;&gt;The Senior Manager, Customer Success is responsible for leading and developing a team of Customer Success Managers for MM EMEA &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;and delivering strong outcomes across customer value, retention, expansion, and payment adoption. This role is accountable not only for team performance and execution, but also for building the management operating model, raising capability across the team, and driving scalable improvements in the post-onboarding customer journey.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;wnfdntt _1ibi0s3f5 _1ibi0s3ce _1ibi0s3ea&quot; data-pm-slice=&quot;1 1 []&quot;&gt;You will lead through managers’ fundamentals and business ownership: setting clear direction, translating regional priorities into execution plans, inspecting performance trends, and coaching your team to deliver consistent results. You will also act as a key partner to the regional Director of Customer Success for Europe and collaborate cross-functionally to improve customer experience, reduce risk, and increase commercial impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;wnfdntt _1ibi0s3f5 _1ibi0s3ce _1ibi0s3ea&quot; data-pm-slice=&quot;1 1 []&quot;&gt;This role manages a distributed team across Europe, including Senior Customer Success Managers, CSMs, and Associate CSMs, and supports customers across multiple regions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;heading 3&quot;&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134245418&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134245529&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:80}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Help make the world more hospitable &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The hospitality industry is uniquely human, and it deserves technology that’s just as inspiring as the people behind it. At Mews, we’re transforming the industry with a platform that helps hotels run smarter, move faster and create better guest experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll work with smart, curious people who care deeply about what they do. You’ll have autonomy and the trust to make good decisions and move quickly. And you’ll enjoy a real sense of purpose as you see the impact of what we’re building.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re motivated by ownership, curiosity and meaningful impact, and are driven to deliver consistent high performance, you’ll feel at home here.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Let&#39;s get into the specifics. It’s impossible to capture every nuance of a role – especially at a rapidly growing company like Mews – but if we had to distil it into a job description (which we do because this is a job description), it would be this:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;wnfdnte&quot; data-pm-slice=&quot;1 1 []&quot;&gt;At Mews, our financial and regulatory data is the backbone of how we close the books, report to investors, satisfy regulators and get IPO‑ready. Right now, that backbone is being tested and we need to make it scalable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;wnfdnte&quot;&gt;We’re looking for a Senior Manager of Data – Finance to take ownership of our finance data world: the pipelines, platforms and practices that turn complex operational, RevOps, Financial Services, billing and core finance data into trusted, auditable, decision‑ready insight.&amp;nbsp;If you love taking something complex, high‑stakes and business‑critical and turning it into a calm, well‑run machine, this one’s for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;wnfdnte&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;✅ Your mission, should you choose to accept it:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;wnfdnte&quot;&gt;Lead and develop the Finance &amp;amp; Regulatory Data team (analytics/data engineers and a data scientist) across Europe.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;wnfdnte&quot;&gt;Own the strategy, architecture and roadmap for Mews’ finance and regulatory data platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;wnfdnte&quot;&gt;Prioritise and deliver data projects that support Corporate Finance, FP&amp;amp;A, Financial Systems, FinTech and RevOps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;wnfdnte&quot;&gt;Raise the bar on data quality, governance, lineage and auditability for all finance and regulatory data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;wnfdnte&quot;&gt;Partner closely with finance and business leaders to translate needs into clear data solutions and narratives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;wnfdnte&quot;&gt;Reduce manual, spreadsheet‑driven processes through automation, advanced analytics and ML‑powered insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;heading 2&quot;&gt;🤝️&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; &lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;heading 2&quot;&gt;You’ll&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;heading 2&quot;&gt; be a great fit if you bring a few of the below with you:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;wnfdnte&quot;&gt;Hands‑on data leader with deep experience in large‑scale data infrastructure (Databricks is ideal; Snowflake or similar lakehouse platforms also great). You’re comfortable diving into architecture and code, even if you’re not shipping every pipeline yourself.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;wnfdnte&quot;&gt;Proven experience in finance‑heavy, regulated or complex environments (SaaS with a strong finance lens is a big plus).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;wnfdnte&quot;&gt;St

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Help make the world more hospitable &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The hospitality industry is uniquely human, and it deserves technology that’s just as inspiring as the people behind it. At Mews, we’re transforming the industry with a platform that helps hotels run smarter, move faster and create better guest experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll work with smart, curious people who care deeply about what they do. You’ll have autonomy and the trust to make good decisions and move quickly. And you’ll enjoy a real sense of purpose as you see the impact of what we’re building.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re motivated by ownership, curiosity and meaningful impact, and are driven to deliver consistent high performance, you’ll feel at home here.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Let&#39;s get into the specifics. It’s impossible to capture every nuance of a role – especially at a rapidly growing company like Mews – but if we had to distil it into a job description (which we do because this is a job description), it would be this:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;21&quot;&gt;At Mews, we&#39;re redefining how hospitality works – and that includes how software gets built. In our &lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Front of House &amp;amp; POS division&lt;/strong&gt;, we&#39;re growing a team of Product Builders: high-agency engineers who shape what gets built, not just how.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;258&quot;&gt;As a &lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Senior Product Builder Mobile (Android)&lt;/strong&gt;, you&#39;ll take end-to-end ownership of product initiatives on the &lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Mews POS&lt;/strong&gt; – a heavy mobile product used daily in real-world hospitality environments. While your primary focus is mobile, you&#39;ll also contribute across &lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;backend and web&lt;/strong&gt; when needed, working as a true full-stack Product Builder. You&#39;ll work closely with Product Managers and Designers to define problems, prototype rapidly and ship impactful solutions – with a strong mobile-first lens.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;752&quot;&gt;This is not a traditional engineering role. It&#39;s a hybrid of builder, maker and product thinker – designed for people who thrive in ambiguity, care deeply about real-world impact and have deep mastery of the Android platform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;✅ Your mission, should you choose to accept it:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;999&quot;&gt;Take &lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;end-to-end ownership&lt;/strong&gt; of product initiatives on the Mews POS Android application – from problem definition to prototype to production.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1141&quot;&gt;Build rapidly, ship often and iterate based on real feedback from hospitality operators.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1233&quot;&gt;Lead the design and implementation of &lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;mobile-first systems&lt;/strong&gt; that power:
&lt;ul class=&quot;ak-ul&quot; data-indent-level=&quot;2&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1307&quot;&gt;Point-of-Sale workflows and real-time transaction processing&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1371&quot;&gt;Hardware integrations (printers, payment terminals, peripherals)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1439&quot;&gt;Offline-capable and resilient mobile experiences&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1491&quot;&gt;AI-powered features and smart automation within the POS product&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1560&quot;&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Help make the world more hospitable &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The hospitality industry is uniquely human, and it deserves technology that’s just as inspiring as the people behind it. At Mews, we’re transforming the industry with a platform that helps hotels run smarter, move faster and create better guest experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll work with smart, curious people who care deeply about what they do. You’ll have autonomy and the trust to make good decisions and move quickly. And you’ll enjoy a real sense of purpose as you see the impact of what we’re building.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re motivated by ownership, curiosity and meaningful impact, and are driven to deliver consistent high performance, you’ll feel at home here.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Let&#39;s get into the specifics. It’s impossible to capture every nuance of a role – especially at a rapidly growing company like Mews – but if we had to distil it into a job description (which we do because this is a job description), it would be this:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We’re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Product Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to join our FinTech team and lead the development of&amp;nbsp;our payment acceptance and&amp;nbsp;acquiring&amp;nbsp;capabilities – the infrastructure that enables thousands of hospitality businesses across multiple markets to accept, process and settle payments seamlessly.&amp;nbsp;This is a role for someone who&amp;nbsp;understands the full lifecycle of a transaction – from authorization through to settlement and reconciliation&amp;nbsp;–&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;who can translate that knowledge into products that create&amp;nbsp;real&amp;nbsp;competitive&amp;nbsp;advantage.&amp;nbsp;You’ll&amp;nbsp;operate&amp;nbsp;end-to-end – from&amp;nbsp;identifying&amp;nbsp;opportunities and shaping strategy, to working closely with engineering and design to bring products to life.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;You’ll&amp;nbsp;be responsible for&amp;nbsp;building scalable&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;compliant solutions that drive&amp;nbsp;transaction volume across a growing number of markets.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;✅ Your mission, should you choose to accept it:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the product lifecycle end-to-end – from discovery through to delivery and iteration.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and drive product strategy for our acquiring and payment acceptance capabilities.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify high-impact opportunities through data, customer insights, and market trends &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with engineering, design, and data teams to deliver high-quality payment solutions &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with stakeholders across the business (Finance, Legal, GTM, Support) to ensure alignment and successful launches &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate complex financial and technical requirements into clear product direction &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive measurable outcomes – adoption, revenue, efficiency, and customer satisfaction &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Navigate regulatory and compliance considerations in a pragmatic, scalable way &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
